snippet: Keuchel, the Astros’ ace who has a signature beard, is hard to categorize, but “command pitcher” may come as close as anything, said his catcher, Jason Castro.
abstract: Houston Astros pitcher Dallas Keuchel has had successful season and is under consideration for Cy Young Award, though experts and fellow players have difficulty figuring out exactly what he is doing right; hopes to live up to expectations in upcoming wild-card game against New York Yankees.
lead_paragraph: Keuchel, the Astros’ ace who has a signature beard, is hard to categorize, but “command pitcher” may come as close as anything, said his catcher, Jason Castro.

headline.print_headline: An Astro’s Key to Success Is as Hidden as His Neck
headline.main: Dallas Keuchel’s Key to Success Is as Hidden as His Neck
